Are you ready to enter the world of the Azzurri?
Download the new SSC Napoli - Official App and stay up to date on all the news about the club: consult the information available on the standings, calendar and results achieved with a simple tap! Don't miss the exclusive experiences of your favorite team!


▶ FEATURES OF THE APP

The SSC Napoli - Official App is your point of reference for all the news and news from the Partenopei, where you can:
- consult the ranking, the calendar and the blue roster;
- stay updated on the formations and the commentary of all the matches;
- read the latest news;
- access exclusive content such as photos and videos of training and matches;
- take photos and selfies with our fan cam and personalize them with our stickers.

And if you are a member of our “Azzurri” membership, you will be able to access super-exclusive digital content, we will send you offers designed especially for you and you will be able to take part in quizzes and surveys.

To find out more, visit our website and follow us on our social channels: Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, TikTok, YouTube and LinkedIn.
